
                About the so-called "gPodder Icon Theme"
                ========================================

This icon theme is a subset of the gnome-icon-theme and the GTK+ stock
icons. Only icons used/referenced in gPodder are available in this theme.

The reason for creating this theme is that some systems (Maemo 4) do not have
a proper icon theme installed, and the stock icons are outdated. Using this
icon theme fixes the issue by providing a complete, up-to-date icon theme.

As a result of combining GPLv2 code with LGPLv2 "or later" code, this icon
theme is released under the terms of the GPLv2 only (see the file "COPYING").

See doc/dev/icon-theme/ in the gPodder source distribution for the scripts
that are used to obtain a list of used images and how to combine them.

